## Step 10: Security Checklist

```
[ ] No room join without membership check ([AUTH-004])
[ ] Token from handshake.auth only — not query.userId
[ ] Live update only for authorized character/campaign
[ ] No PII/token in WS logs
[ ] CORS origin = FRONTEND_URL
```

