## Anti-patterns

- ❌ Broadcasting before DB commit
- ❌ Client emits live field changes directly (server must validate PATCH)
- ❌ Joining room without authorization
- ❌ localStorage token for WS auth
- ❌ Adding dice/initiative events (MVP scope)
- ❌ kebab-case violation (`joinCampaign` instead of `join-campaign`)

## Member Join/Leave Broadcast

When player joins via invite or removed by DM:

```typescript
// CampaignsService after member add
this.websocketGateway.broadcastMemberJoined(campaignId, {
  userId: member.userId,
  username: member.user.username,
  avatarUrl: member.user.avatarUrl,
});
```

Emit **after** DB transaction commits.

## Token Refresh During Session

Access token expires (15 min). On refresh, reconnect socket with new token:

```typescript
// After auth slice receives new accessToken
disconnectSocket();
connectSocket(newAccessToken);
socket.emit('join-campaign', { campaignId });
```

Document in `docs/05` if refresh flow changes.

## DM Screen REST + WS Dual Path

| Action | Channel |
| --- | --- |
| User edits live field | REST `PATCH /characters/:id/live` |
| Other clients update | WS `character:live-update` |
| Initial page load | REST GET characters — not WS history |

WS is push-only for live fields — no event sourcing replay in MVP.

## Scaling Notes

Redis adapter mandatory when `instances > 1`. Local dev single instance works without adapter but keep code path for parity.

## Environment Variables

```
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379
JWT_ACCESS_SECRET=...  # same as HTTP JWT verify
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:5173  # gateway CORS
```

## Troubleshooting

| Symptom | Check |
| --- | --- |
| WS connects then disconnects | Token expired/invalid; `isActive` user |
| Updates only on one tab | Redis adapter not connected |
| Player sees DM notes | Wrong route guard — not WS issue |
| CORS error | `FRONTEND_URL` matches Vite origin |
| Event not received | Client joined room? `join-campaign` ack `joined-campaign` |

